Package: linux-headers-ec2
Architecture: i386 amd64
Section: devel
Priority: optional
Depends: linux-headers-${kernel-abi-version}-ec2
Description: Linux kernel headers for ec2 machines
 This package will always depend on the latest kernel headers available
 for ec2 machines (which are the same headers as for the server flavour).

Package: linux-image-ec2
Architecture: i386 amd64
Section: metapackages
Priority: optional
Depends: linux-image-${kernel-abi-version}-ec2, linux-firmware
Description: Linux kernel image for ec2 machines
 This package will always depend on the latest kernel image available
 for ec2 machines.

Package: linux-ec2
Architecture: i386 amd64
Section: metapackages
Priority: optional
Depends: linux-image-ec2 (= ${binary:Version})
Description: Complete Linux kernel for ec2 machines
 This package will always depend on the latest complete Linux kernel available
 for ec2 machines.
